      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:07",
        "end_time": "0:08",
        "text": "News for kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:09",
        "end_time": "0:09",
        "text": "真的假的?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:09",
        "end_time": "0:10",
        "text": "真的假的?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:10",
        "end_time": "0:11",
        "text": "真的假的?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:11",
        "end_time": "0:12",
        "text": "原來"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:14",
        "end_time": "0:14",
        "text": "不止"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:14",
        "end_time": "0:16",
        "text": "你不知道的趣味新鮮事"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:16",
        "end_time": "0:19",
        "text": "ICRT News for kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:21",
        "end_time": "0:23",
        "text": "The earth needs a lot of help."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:23",
        "end_time": "0:24",
        "text": "Who can help?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:25",
        "end_time": "0:28",
        "text": "One man says kids can help the earth."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:29",
        "end_time": "0:32",
        "text": "有個人說小朋友可以幫助地球"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:33",
        "end_time": "0:35",
        "text": "The man made a game for kids."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:35",
        "end_time": "0:38",
        "text": "The game helps them save the earth."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:39",
        "end_time": "0:42",
        "text": "In this game, kids are superheroes."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:47",
        "end_time": "0:50",
        "text": "他为小朋友设计了一个救地球的游戏。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:51",
        "end_time": "0:54",
        "text": "在游戏里,他们都是超级英雄。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:55",
        "end_time": "0:57",
        "text": "How do kids play the game?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:57",
        "end_time": "1:00",
        "text": "First, they make a superhero group."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:02",
        "end_time": "1:04",
        "text": "Superheroes are stronger together."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:04",
        "end_time": "1:07",
        "text": "这个游戏该怎么玩呢?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:07",
        "end_time": "1:11",
        "text": "首先,小朋友们要组成超级英雄联盟。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:20",
        "end_time": "1:31",
        "text": "他们找找看家里附近,有没有可以帮助地球的,公园干不干净,是不是没有树或花园。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:31",
        "end_time": "1:39",
        "text": "他们找找看家里附近,有没有可以帮助地球的,公园干不干净,是不是没有树或花园。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:39",
        "end_time": "1:43",
        "text": "超级英雄们和邻居聊过"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:43",
        "end_time": "1:44",
        "text": "他们学到很多"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:44",
        "end_time": "1:48",
        "text": "有一些邻居还给他们很多帮助"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:48",
        "end_time": "1:51",
        "text": "超级英雄们有很多想法"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:51",
        "end_time": "1:52",
        "text": "他们计划"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:52",
        "end_time": "1:54",
        "text": "然后"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:54",
        "end_time": "1:57",
        "text": "超级英雄们开玩笑"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:57",
        "end_time": "1:59",
        "text": "孩子们有很多的想法"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:59",
        "end_time": "2:01",
        "text": "他们订了一个计划"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:01",
        "end_time": "2:04",
        "text": "超级英雄们把公园做得干净"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:15",
        "end_time": "2:24",
        "text": "他们绿化了公园,也把它变干净。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:24",
        "end_time": "2:28",
        "text": "他们玩得很开心,还帮助了地球。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:28",
        "end_time": "2:31",
        "text": "地球需要很多超级英雄。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:31",
        "end_time": "2:34",
        "text": "你和你的朋友也可以成为超级英雄。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:35",
        "end_time": "2:36",
        "text": "一起玩游戏吧!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:37",
        "end_time": "2:40",
        "text": "地球需要更多的超级英雄。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:40",
        "end_time": "2:41",
        "text": "你和你的朋友可以成为超级英雄。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:41",
        "end_time": "2:41",
        "text": "一起玩游戏吧!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:41",
        "end_time": "2:41",
        "text": "地球需要更多的超级英雄。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:41",
        "end_time": "2:44",
        "text": "也一起參加遊戲吧"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:46",
        "end_time": "2:47",
        "text": "一個好玩的遊戲"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:47",
        "end_time": "2:50",
        "text": "讓兒童幫地球的忙"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:50",
        "end_time": "2:52",
        "text": "dirty 髒的"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:52",
        "end_time": "2:57",
        "text": "哇 這個海灘真是髒"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:57",
        "end_time": "3:04",
        "text": "是啊 我小時候不是這樣的"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:04",
        "end_time": "3:07",
        "text": "look at 看或是注視"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:07",
        "end_time": "3:10",
        "text": "Look at all these bottles and bags."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:11",
        "end_time": "3:12",
        "text": "你看这些瓶子袋子。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:13",
        "end_time": "3:14",
        "text": "Should we help clean this beach?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:15",
        "end_time": "3:17",
        "text": "我们应该帮忙清理这个海滩吗?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:18",
        "end_time": "3:20",
        "text": "Neighborhood, 临近的区域。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:21",
        "end_time": "3:26",
        "text": "No, what we should do is get everyone in this neighborhood to help out."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:26",
        "end_time": "3:30",
        "text": "不,我们应该做的是让这个地方每个人都来帮忙清理。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:30",
        "end_time": "3:31",
        "text": "That's too hard."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:32",
        "end_time": "3:33",
        "text": "那太难了。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:33",
        "end_time": "3:35",
        "text": "Together, 一起。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:35",
        "end_time": "3:38",
        "text": "I know, but it's the only way."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:38",
        "end_time": "3:40",
        "text": "我知道,不過這是唯一的辦法。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:41",
        "end_time": "3:43",
        "text": "And it can be fun when people do it together."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:44",
        "end_time": "3:46",
        "text": "而且大家一起做,還會很好玩呢。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:47",
        "end_time": "3:49",
        "text": "一起來讀今天的單字。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:49",
        "end_time": "3:50",
        "text": "Dirty,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:51",
