        "text": "What?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:03",
        "end_time": "0:03",
        "text": "No!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:03",
        "end_time": "0:04",
        "text": "Yes way!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:04",
        "end_time": "0:05",
        "text": "It's time for..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:05",
        "end_time": "0:06",
        "text": "News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:07",
        "end_time": "0:08",
        "text": "News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:08",
        "end_time": "0:09",
        "text": "真的假的!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:09",
        "end_time": "0:10",
        "text": "真的假的!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:10",
        "end_time": "0:10",
        "text": "真的假的!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:11",
        "end_time": "0:12",
        "text": "原來如此!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:13",
        "end_time": "0:16",
        "text": "不止你不知道的趣味新鮮事"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:16",
        "end_time": "0:18",
        "text": "ICRT's News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:20",
        "end_time": "0:21",
        "text": "Do you like animals?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:21",
        "end_time": "0:22",
        "text": "Cats?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:22",
        "end_time": "0:23",
        "text": "Dogs?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:24",
        "end_time": "0:25",
        "text": "How about monkeys?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:26",
        "end_time": "0:30",
        "text": "One scientist likes Northern Muraki monkeys."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:30",
        "end_time": "0:33",
        "text": "She likes their cinnamon smell too."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:33",
        "end_time": "0:37",
        "text": "她喜欢研究这些猴子。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:37",
        "end_time": "0:43",
        "text": "有一位科学家喜欢北戎毛猪猴,也喜欢研究它们。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:43",
        "end_time": "0:48",
        "text": "北戎毛猪猴是北美和南美最大的猴子。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:48",
        "end_time": "0:51",
        "text": "它们大约150厘米。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:52",
        "end_time": "0:54",
        "text": "它们大约15公斤。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:54",
        "end_time": "0:58",
        "text": "它们的尖头很长,而且很强。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:58",
        "end_time": "1:01",
        "text": "它们的尖头能让它们从树到树走。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:01",
        "end_time": "1:10",
        "text": "这种猴子是美洲最大的猴子,身高150公分,体重15公斤,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:11",
        "end_time": "1:16",
        "text": "长长的尾巴,让它们可以从一棵树挡到另外一棵树。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:17",
        "end_time": "1:19",
        "text": "MOST MONKEYS FIGHT"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:19",
        "end_time": "1:22",
        "text": "But Northern Murakie are very peaceful."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:23",
        "end_time": "1:23",
        "text": "They don't fight."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:24",
        "end_time": "1:26",
        "text": "They hug each other a lot."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:26",
        "end_time": "1:28",
        "text": "People call them hippie monkeys."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:29",
        "end_time": "1:31",
        "text": "这种猴子非常温和。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:32",
        "end_time": "1:35",
        "text": "他们不会吵架,会互相抱抱。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:35",
        "end_time": "1:39",
        "text": "The scientist studies these murakie, but she is trying to save them too."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:40",
        "end_time": "1:42",
        "text": "They are in very big danger."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:43",
        "end_time": "1:45",
        "text": "这位科学家也努力拯救他们。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:45",
        "end_time": "1:49",
        "text": "因為他們現在瀕臨絕種"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:49",
        "end_time": "1:51",
        "text": "一百萬的北榮毛族猴"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:51",
        "end_time": "1:54",
        "text": "在森林裡住了一段長時間"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:55",
        "end_time": "1:58",
        "text": "但人們把棵樹切下來了"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:59",
        "end_time": "2:01",
        "text": "他們想要做森林"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:01",
        "end_time": "2:05",
        "text": "森林越來越小了"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:06",
        "end_time": "2:09",
        "text": "現在只有一千個北榮毛族猴"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:09",
        "end_time": "2:12",
        "text": "人們仍然把棵樹切下來了"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:12",
        "end_time": "2:13",
        "text": "很久以前"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:13",
        "end_time": "2:17",
        "text": "森林裡有一百萬隻北榮毛族猴"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:18",
        "end_time": "2:26",
        "text": "但人类砍了很多树,森林变得越来越小,现在只剩下一千只。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:26",
        "end_time": "2:31",
        "text": "When forests are too small, there can be no Northern Murakie."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:31",
        "end_time": "2:34",
        "text": "森林变太小,就会没有它们了。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:34",
        "end_time": "2:38",
        "text": "The scientist has been helping the Northern Murakie for 40 years now."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:39",
        "end_time": "2:40",
        "text": "She doesn't want to stop."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:41",
        "end_time": "2:42",
        "text": "There is a lot to do."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:43",
        "end_time": "2:43",
